			======================================
				 Installing libavfltctl
			======================================

1. Requirements
	
	* Installed RedirFS Control Library - librfsctl, please see the
	  librfsctl INSTALL file

2. Download
	
	* Get the latest stable version at
	  http://www.redirfs.org/packages/libavfltctl-x.y.z.tar.gz

3. Compilation
	
	* Unpack package
		$ tar -xvzf libavfltctl-x.y.z.tar.gz

	* Change to the libavfltctl-x.y.z directory
		$ cd libavfltctl-x.y.z

	* Run make command
		$ make

4. Installation/Uninstallation

	* Change user to root
		$ su

	* Install libavfltctl 
		# make install

	* Uninstall libavfltctl
		# make uninstall

5. Problems & Bugs

	* RedirFS's bugzilla
	  http://www.redirfs.org/cgi-bin/bugzilla/index.cgi
	
	* RedirFS's mailing lists
	  http://www.redirfs.org/tiki-index.php?page=redirfs_maillists
